Comment: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:04.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.01,0:00:39.39,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\org(489,186)\move(567,238,501,196)\fax-0.1\c&H69452A&\fnA-OTF Shin Go Pro M\frz354.6\blur0.8\t(0,3380,\fscx118\fscy118)\frx1\fry-3\fs36}If you want to kill me,\Nthen come and do it. I'll\Nbe waiting with the door\Nopen. I'll kill YOU instead.\N- Daisaku Katsumoto
Dialogue: 1,0:00:39.39,0:00:41.02,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\org(489,186)\move(501,196,461,172)\fscx118\fscy118\fax-0.1\c&H69452A&\fnA-OTF Shin Go Pro M\frz354.6\blur0.8\t(0,1630,\fscx129\fscy129)\frx1\fry-3\fs36}If you want to kill me,\Nthen come and do it. I'll\Nbe waiting with the door\Nopen. I'll kill YOU instead.\N- Daisaku Katsumoto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:43.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}It doesn't matter how many times you try,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:45.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}whether it's in love, cases, today, or tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:48.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}A mass e-mail sent just before a fatal fall... Was it a trick to hide a murderer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:50.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:52.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:55.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Sorry, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}, but it seems Dad won't be able to drive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He was up drinking until past 5 AM, so he's still sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I apologise, but could you and Ai-{\i1}chan{\i0} take the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Okay, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.25,0:02:58.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:02:59.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:04.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Now I think about it, the old man wasn't in bed when I got up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:08.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Looks like the Kogorō-{\i1}san{\i0} rental car plan failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:11.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Crap, and it's already seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Even if we go back to the bus stop now, the ski bus with the doc and the kids are on will have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That's why I said that since {\i1}I{\i0} forgot something, I should've come back and got it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:28.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Idiot! I came with you as a child wandering about alone is just asking to be kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:31.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Though I'm not a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:33.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}You still {\i1}look{\i0} like one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.47,0:03:35.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.47,0:03:40.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}We could go by train, but we'd have to wait ages switching trains,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}and it'll be evening by the time we got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Can't help it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:46.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's not we have any other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}We could have Subaru-{\i1}san{\i0} drive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}B-But is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Why not? He always seems to have tons of time to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:04:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I meant is it okay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Didn't you hate him or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:05.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I can't always be so choosy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:07.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Like I said, I'm not a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But you {\i1}look{\i0} like—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:12.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Though I guess that doesn't matter here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:16.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}And perhaps he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Okay, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:26.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Stop being so noisy first thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:31.04,CharCards,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,560)\fad(250,0)}Daisaku Katsumoto (58)\NPublishing Company President
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:31.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\a6\blur1}Oh, it's you... So you actually turned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Well, come in, I may as well hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Though I doubt you've anything of interest to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, so you're all going skiing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:48.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}As I happen to be going, I may as well try some skiing too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:51.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I feel like my body's a bit out of shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:55.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Why, is there some reason you need to stay fit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:05:00.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Well, I would like to impress the ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Detective Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Were you on a stakeout?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Chiba just took over for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:17.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'm glad to see you're back to work so soon though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:22.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yeah... Though I still dream about it sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I always wake up the moment I fall off the plank though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'm always telling myself, 'you're okay, you didn't fall, you didn't fall...'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:35.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:36.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Someone fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:39.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Get an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:40.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Was that from the other side of this block?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:42.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Get in, Detective Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:44.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Let's take a look at the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.75,0:05:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Come on, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:52.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I... couldn't help but look...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:54.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:59.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'm with the police. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:06.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:12.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I happened to pass by here when I was jogging,{\blur1} and suddenly this man fell from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I saw it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}This street's on my dogwalking course...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:19.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}So he fell from this block of flats?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:22.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Does anyone know who this man is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:28.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He has a mobile phone in his shirt pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:31.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Ah, you're right.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.49,0:06:37.71,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(473,292)\blur0.6\fax0.1\c&H8D6E56&\fs26\fnA-OTF Shin Go Pro M\frz0.92}- Daisaku Katsumoto
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.49,0:06:37.71,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(461,248)\blur0.6\fax0.1\c&H8D6E56&\fs26\fnA-OTF Shin Go Pro M\frz0.97}kill YOU instead.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.49,0:06:37.71,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(453,216)\blur0.6\fax0.1\c&H8D6E56&\fs26\fnA-OTF Shin Go Pro M\frz0.97}then come and do it. I'll
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.49,0:06:37.71,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(449,185)\blur0.6\fax0.1\c&H8D6E56&\fs26\fnA-OTF Shin Go Pro M\frz0.97}If you want to kill me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Looks like he sent an odd e-mail just before falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:42.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And also, it was transmitted simultaneously to a number of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Then why don't we try resending it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:47.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hey, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It seems it was sent to those three.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:07:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Which means you all must know the man that fell, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:03.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Why didn't you say anything earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:10.86,CharCards,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,560)\fad(250,0)}Keisuke Ogino (34)\NCameraman
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:10.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\a6\blur1}Well... I'd only just rushed out of my flat after hearing some screams, and I hadn't been able to see his face yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:17.58,CharCards,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,560)\fad(250,0)}Kaori Tsukihara (28)\NMagazine Editor
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:13.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\a6\blur1}M-Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:17.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\a6\blur1}Someone yelled so loud that I spilt the coffee I was drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:23.88,CharCards,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,560)\fad(250,0)}Kazutomo Sodesaki (31)\NWriter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\a6\blur1}I also came here since I heard someone cry out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:23.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\a6\blur1}But if the man who fell was the one sent the e-mail earlier, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:26.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}it must be President Katsumoto that fell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:27.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:28.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He was a company president?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:32.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He was Daisaku Katsumoto, the president and editor-in-chief of Katsumoto Publishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:41.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You must've heard of 'Weekly Great', the magazine that's been selling more and more copies lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:45.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yeah... I've heard it's full of things like celebrity gossip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The company president lives in the same building as his employees?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:52.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's just a coincidence, it's because the company building's nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:56.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I've been intending to move for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.43,0:07:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'm a freelancer, not an employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Well, the three of us live on the third floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.47,0:08:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}and the president on the twenty-sixth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:08.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Well then, could you accompany me to the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}There's various things we'll need to ask you about...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:14.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hey, wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:15.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Are you suspecting us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}We just said we were all in our own flats until it happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:22.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But is there anyone who can prove that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:27.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I guess not... All three of us live by ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:33.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Then let's take a look at their flats now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:36.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's been less than four minutes since we heard someone shouting 'He fell!'.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}We may be able to figure something out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:50.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I wonder what they hope to figure out by seeing their flats...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:53.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Considering the injuries on the corpse,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}it seems he fell from quite a high floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:09:00.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}If this was a murder, the killer probably pushed the victim from inside his flat,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}then rushed here straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:09.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}If there's any trace that they were just in their flats, they'll be cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:12.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}They're only able to see their flats straight away
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:15.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}as Detective Takagi happened to be close to the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:22.20,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,{\blur1}Since this situation would be impossible for the killer to predict, they wouldn't have had any need to return to their flat after the crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}and orchestrate that they were in there until just before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:30.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You certainly seem to know a lot about murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Of course! I'm a Sherlockian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:37.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But what interests me is not the murders, but their solutions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:39.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:49.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So, Tsukihara-{\i1}san{\i0} and Sodesaki-{\i1}san{\i0}, could you both wait by the entrance with the door open?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:50.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:10:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What's that bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:05.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's an attendance gift I got when leaving a funeral recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:10.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So, do you have any way to prove you were here until not long ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:15.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}L-Look, the TV's still on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:18.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That's not quite good evidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:21.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Ah, this is good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:24.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}There's still all this froth left on my beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'd been watching TV while drinking it until just before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:29.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Something that could prove I was here until recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Do I have anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.31,0:10:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You went to the same funeral as Ogino-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yeah, all three of us went.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Though the president didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:49.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Umm... About this coffee...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, that's the coffee I was drinking just before I left the flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I can't get going in the mornings until I've had my daily coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:11:02.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Then this could potentially be evidence, couldn't it? There's still steam faintly coming from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:06.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hurry up, Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hurry up and look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Come on, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:14.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}When I heard about the steam from Tsukihara-{\i1}san{\i0}'s coffee, I remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh no, it's already out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:23.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I left a cigarette I'd just started smoking in the ashtray right before leaving,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.81,0:11:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}so I thought it'd still be lit...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:31.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}See, there's still smoke rising from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}This is proof I was here not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I-Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So none of you three went to the president's flat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:41.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:42.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That's what we've been telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:52.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}So the elements proving their alibis are froth, steam and smoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:02.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Froth, steam and smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Their alibis are based on such unreliable things?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yes. Let me explain everything step by step.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}At around 7:30 AM, on my way back to the station after finishing my shift at a stakeout,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:20.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I heard people screaming that someone had fallen down, and rushed to the front of this block.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:23.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I found a man dressed in a gown and pyjamas lying on the pavement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:28.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}From speaking to witnesses, I found out he had fallen from one of the topmost floors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:33.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}There was a mobile phone inside the breast pocket of his pyjamas,
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.94,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(473,292)\blur0.6\fax0.1\c&H8D6E56&\fs26\fnA-OTF Shin Go Pro M\frz0.92}- Daisaku Katsumoto
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.94,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(461,248)\blur0.6\fax0.1\c&H8D6E56&\fs26\fnA-OTF Shin Go Pro M\frz0.97}kill YOU instead.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.94,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(453,216)\blur0.6\fax0.1\c&H8D6E56&\fs26\fnA-OTF Shin Go Pro M\frz0.97}then come and do it. I'll
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.94,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(449,185)\blur0.6\fax0.1\c&H8D6E56&\fs26\fnA-OTF Shin Go Pro M\frz0.97}If you want to kill me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:38.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}and when I checked it, I found he'd sent a mass e-mail at 7:25 AM, just before falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So I attempted sending the same e-mail again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:46.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So these three received that inflammatory e-mail designed to encourage the killer to act, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:57.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The man who fell was the president of a publishing company
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:13:01.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}that those three work for, Daisaku Katsumoto-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:09.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The content of the e-mail being what it was, I thought about having them come to the police station to question them,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}but realised that if I went into their flats straight away,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}there may be some evidence proving they were in there until just before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So you went into their flats,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}and froth on beer, steam from a cup of coffee,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}and a cigarette's smoke were what they showed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:25.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:33.97,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,{\blur1}If one of the three had pushed Katsumoto off and then hid among the crowd,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:37.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}he or she would have had to come straight here without taking any detours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:47.64,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,{\blur1}As the sooner they were seen here, the more believable a claim they'd rushed here after hearing the commotion would be during questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:52.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But you're the only one who saw the froth, steam and smoke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:53.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I made sure to take some pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Though they're with my mobile phone camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:13:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}C-Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:06.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I came across him and his friends in their car {\blur1}when I heard the 'He fell!' shouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:14.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So you're telling me you took Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0} with you into the flat of somebody who might be a murderer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:16.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:19.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Actually, it was Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s idea to visit the flats right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:21.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hey, take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}This is Ogino-{\i1}san{\i0}'s beer's froth,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:29.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}this is Tsukihara-{\i1}san{\i0}'s steaming coffee,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:32.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}which I recorded a video of since it'd be hard to see in a photo,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}and this is Sodesaki-{\i1}san{\i0}'s cigarette smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:41.65,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,{\blur1}I asked each of them to hold their evidence when I took the picture so you could tell which was from which room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Where were the other two suspects while you were taking these photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:50.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I asked them to wait outside each flat with the door left open,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}so none of them had time to sneak into their respective flats to make up their alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:15:02.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So, president Katsumoto was pushed off his balcony on the 26th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Both the front door and the window to the balcony were left open.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It seems that right after sending the e-mail, the president called an interior construction company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}An interior construction company?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:17.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}They remodelled his flat last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:23.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}but it appears the carpet put in was not the one he had ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}While on the phone, the president actually measured the length of the carpet's pile and complained about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}While he was on the phone, the doorbell rang, {\blur1}so he said he'd call them back and hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So president Katsumoto was in his own flat right until he was pushed off the balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And it's safe to assume it was his killer who rang the doorbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}By the way, how long does it take to go from the suspects' flats to the president's?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:58.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}All three of them reside on the third floor, and the president's flat is twenty-three floors above that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}so a round trip should take about seven minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I tried timing myself using the stairs, so I have no doubts about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The stairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.06,0:16:10.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Why didn't you use the lifts instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:13.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The lifts are fitted with surveillance cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I had the control room show me the footage from them,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}and none of the suspects appeared in the footage around 7:30 AM, when president Katsumoto fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:28.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}If one of them was the killer, they'd have had to take the stairs, which don't have surveillance cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:30.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Ringing the president's doorbell...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Pushing him off after having been invited into his flat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:39.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And then leaving to rush down to the ground floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Then by the time you entered their flats after the incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}if one of them was the killer, their room would've been left unoccupied for more than ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:56.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yes, and I think ten minutes is enough time for any froth, steam or smoke to have disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:57.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:17:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But why did the president send that e-mail to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.17,0:17:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Because of the lawsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The three of us were planning to sue him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:09.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}At the beginning of next month, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Sue him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Haven't you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Last week, a famous actress committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:24.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh... If I recall, she killed herself because she made the news kissing her lover, a dangerous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:26.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I took the photo of that kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:28.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I was the one who wrote the article.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And I apparently edited it and published it in Weekly Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:36.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Huh? Apparently?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:39.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yeah, the photo and the articles were complete lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:46.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The photo was taken as they were about to hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}They weren't kissing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The background he was given in the article was also faked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:57.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He was a stuntman, and the facial injuries he had were resulting from shooting that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:18:01.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But that woman was engaged to a young actor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:06.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Still, if they were hugging each other, then I guess it wasn't completely made-up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:08.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That's a wrong assumption as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:13.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He was her younger half-brother, and they hugged because she told him she was engaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Then, why did...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}We learnt the story was false before it was published, so it was scrapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But president Katsumoto rewrote the whole thing and put it back in without anybody's permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:30.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}With a headline of 'Popular actress caught in a late-night dangerous affair before her wedding'!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The magazine was released the day before the press conference for their wedding,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}so it sold like hotcakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:43.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}One of her rabid fans \Nattacked her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:46.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Even now, he's still in hospital, unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:53.18,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,{\blur1}Of course, the marriage was cancelled. And in her despair, she chose to commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:59.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But if she had revealed the truth straight away, wouldn't everyone realise the article was faked...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:01.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}She couldn't say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:05.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Her brother was born out of an affair her father had!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Well, we're sure the president faked the article knowing she couldn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But we can't forgive him for releasing that article with our names on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But we can't forgive him for releasing that article with our names on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:21.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That's why, last night, we sent him an e-mail signed by all three of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Saying we had proof he'd fabricated the article, so he'd better prepare himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.90,0:19:30.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And that we'd sue him until he had nothing left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:32.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So, upon reading the e-mail you sent him this morning, he sent that inflammatory response to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Then those funeral bags in each of your flats, could they be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:47.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Those were gifts for attending that actress's funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Though we had to give fake names and say we were some of her agency's employees.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:20:02.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}If the motive for the murder was that article, shouldn't we consider her relatives to be suspects as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:07.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But the murder happened almost immediately after the president sent the e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:11.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So we can't exactly remove these three from our suspect list...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:12.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}That much is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:15.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}The timing is too good to be a coincidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:21.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}but that froth, steam and smoke prove those three couldn't have committed the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:24.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I thought we could find something by going into each of their flats right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:27.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}not giving them enough time to fabricate an alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:29.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Or {\i1}is{\i0} there really something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:32.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Is there a way to forge evidence in an instant?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:37.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:41.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}When're you going to get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}We've already started skiing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:46.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Give us a call once you're here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:47.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}We'll be waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:52.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Sorry, but we ended up involved in a case, so I don't think we can come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:57.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s saying he can't come because of a case!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:20:59.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So Haibara-{\i1}san{\i0} won't be coming, either?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:00.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Forget that case and come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:05.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's great out here, you can even see your breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:07.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yeah, it's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.04,0:21:09.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}See your breath...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Sorry, I'll call you back later!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:13.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:15.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He hung up...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.08,0:21:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hey, Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Since you're here and all, how about an experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:22.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}An experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:25.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}An experiment with froth, steam and smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.35,0:22:56.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What do you think his plans are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:22:57.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:22:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I mean about the skiing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.17,0:23:01.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Dr. Agasa and the children are waiting for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh... We probably have to cancel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The call he just received was probably from the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:14.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He probably said we got ourselves involved in a case and couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.24,0:23:15.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}As usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I see... What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.12,0:23:24.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So you can go back home now, as we no longer need to be taken anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.15,0:23:28.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}No, it's fine. I'm interested in the result of the case, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:36.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Besides, I can't just leave a frail lady on her own. Especially when a killer could still be on the prowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.52,0:23:40.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You're not exactly a reliable guardian knight, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.16,0:23:42.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That's a harsh thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'll protect you with my own life...{same line Akai said in 675's flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.40,0:23:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.70,0:24:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}A trick hides among the uncertain alibis of the three suspects.{null.AR: ３人の容疑者の不確かなアリバイ しかしそれにはあるトリックが }
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.25,0:24:08.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}On the next Conan: 'Froth, Steam and Smoke (Part II)'!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.71,0:24:13.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Next Conan's Hint: Tools of the trade!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.68,0:24:15.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Should I call Mouri-{\i1}san{\i0} for the experiment?{null.AR: 毛利さん事件に御見ます？ }
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.86,0:24:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Mouri-{\i1}kun{\i0}'d drink the beer, so of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.97,0:24:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Right. {null.AR: うん}
